# Genesis Creation Week, day-04-luminaries-time (problem fragment): lights govern days, seasons, and years.
# One admitted PDDL Turtle planning artifact. Days are planning sources, not
# workflows: every fragment shares the domain name 'creation-week' and merges
# structurally into ONE combined seven-day plan whose projection is the one
# creation-week POWL v2 workflow. Formal process example; argues no doctrine,
# claims no historicity.
@prefix ex: <http://example.org/genesis#> .
@prefix ceng: <urn:chatman:engine#> .

ex:day-04-luminaries-time a ex:CreationDay ;
  ex:daySequence 4 ;
  ex:intends ex:appoint-luminaries .

ex:day-04-luminaries-time ceng:pddlProblem """
(define (problem creation-week-day-04-luminaries-time)
  (:domain creation-week)
  (:objects creation)
  (:init (formless-void creation))
  (:goal (luminaries-appointed creation))
)
""" .
